title: Little hit, big win; Royals beat Jays for 2-0 lead in ALCS
text: Little hit, big win; Royals beat Jays for 2-0 lead in ALCS Sunday, 18 October 2015 (12 minutes ago) KANSAS CITY, Missouri (AP) " Kansas City's dormant bats sprang to life with a five-run seventh inning that rallied the Royals from a three-run deficit to a 6-3 victory over Toronto on Saturday, delivering a 2-0 lead in the best-of-seven...
